Title: Build .NET MAUI apps with GitHub Actions
Description: Building a cross platform .NET MAUI app for Android, iOS, MacCatalyst and Windows with GitHub Actions is complicated. I explain each step in the process.

Title: Why rails buckle in Britain - Network Rail
Description: Why don’t rails get hot in Europe? The truth is they do.

Title: State of the SqueakPhone—Syndicated Actors
Description:
One of my projects over the past couple of years has been Synit, a
Syndicate init (really, systemd and D-Bus) replacement. Synit underpins another
project, #squeak-phone, a sketch of an alternative to Android for personal computing on a
mobile device.
